 which is my stake address 1;


 2 - CREATE SHELLEY TX in ALLEGRA ERA

 Create a second payment key pair and address


 To create our transaction we need the protocol parameters

 cardano-cli query protocol-parameters --allegra-era \
     --testnet-magic 3 \
     --out-file protocol.json


  cardano-cli query utxo --address "$(cat payment.addr)" --testnet-magic  3 --allegra-era
                            TxHash                                 TxIx        Amount
  --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  767ce99448762d02b16b86c2e6d68c92e6975eea28922936384f541caea5e225     0        1000000000000 lovelace



 Draft the SHELLEY transaction in ALLEGRA

 cardano-cli transaction build-raw --shelley-era \
 --tx-in 767ce99448762d02b16b86c2e6d68c92e6975eea28922936384f541caea5e225#0 \
 --tx-out $(cat byron-payment.addr)+0 \
 --tx-out $(cat payment.addr)+0 \
 --ttl 0 \
 --fee 0 \
 --out-file tx.draft


 cardano-cli transaction calculate-min-fee \
 --tx-body-file tx.draft \
 --tx-in-count 1 \
 --tx-out-count 2 \
 --witness-count 1 \
 --byron-witness-count 0 \
 --testnet-magic 12 \
 --protocol-params-file protocol.json

 176061 Lovelace

 Calculate the change to send back to payment.addr

 expr 1000000000000 - 10000000000 - 176061
 989999823939


 cardano-cli query tip --testnet-magic 3
