3 - CREATE SHELLEY TX with METADATA in ALLEGRA ERA

Draft the SHELLEY transaction in ALLEGRA ERA

cardano-cli query utxo --address "$(cat payment.addr)" --testnet-magic  3 --allegra-era
                           TxHash                                 TxIx        Amount
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
7f5010f5d2db91f206a78af570197f157f4c7372db3ef13470cdfbcdebf576b1     1        989999823939 lovelace



cardano-cli transaction build-raw --shelley-era \
--tx-in 7f5010f5d2db91f206a78af570197f157f4c7372db3ef13470cdfbcdebf576b1#1 \
--tx-out $(cat extended-payment.addr)+0 \
--tx-out $(cat payment.addr)+0 \
--ttl 0 \
--fee 0 \
--out-file tx.draft


cardano-cli transaction calculate-min-fee \
--tx-body-file tx.draft \
--tx-in-count 1 \
--tx-out-count 2 \
--witness-count 1 \
--byron-witness-count 0 \
--testnet-magic 3 \
--protocol-params-file protocol.json

176545 Lovelace

QUESTION - why fee is being calculated wrong ?

Calculate the change to send back to payment.addr

expr 989999823939 - 100000000000 - 183849
889999640090


cardano-cli query tip --testnet-magic 3
{
    "blockNo": 476688,
    "headerHash": "2ca54cb667c10cbc378a3efcc7bd43138849a5dc619da9b00484d99c571375f6",
    "slotNo": 9921880
}


A - attempt to use invalid upper bound set in the past

cardano-cli transaction build-raw --shelley-era \
--tx-in 7f5010f5d2db91f206a78af570197f157f4c7372db3ef13470cdfbcdebf576b1#1 \
--tx-out $(cat extended-payment.addr)+100000000000 \
--tx-out $(cat payment.addr)+889999640090 \
--invalid-hereafter 3921880 \
--fee 183849 \
--metadata-json-file metadata.json \
--metadata-json-file metadata2.json \
--metadata-cbor-file metadata3.cbor \
--metadata-cbor-file metadata4.cbor \
--out-file tx002.raw



cardano-cli transaction sign \
--tx-body-file tx002.raw \
--signing-key-file ../keys/payment.skey \
--testnet-magic 3 \
--out-file tx002.signed


cardano-cli transaction submit \
--tx-file tx002.signed \
--testnet-magic 3


Shelley command failed: transaction submit  Error: Error while submitting tx: ApplyTxError [LedgerFailure (UtxowFailure (UtxoFailure (OutsideValidityIntervalUTxO (ValidityInterval {validFrom = SNothing, validTo = SJust (SlotNo 3921880)}) (SlotNo 9921961))))]

B - attempt to use lower bound for shelley ERA

cardano-cli transaction build-raw --shelley-era \
--tx-in 7f5010f5d2db91f206a78af570197f157f4c7372db3ef13470cdfbcdebf576b1#1 \
--tx-out $(cat extended-payment.addr)+100000000000 \
--tx-out $(cat payment.addr)+889999647878 \
--invalid-before 159640 \
--fee 176061 \
--metadata-json-file metadata.json \
--metadata-json-file metadata2.json \
--metadata-cbor-file metadata3.cbor \
--metadata-cbor-file metadata4.cbor \
--out-file tx002.raw

Shelley command failed: transaction build-raw  Error: A validity lower bound cannot be used for Shelley era transactions.


C - valid shelley TX in allegra ERA

cardano-cli transaction build-raw --shelley-era \
--tx-in 7f5010f5d2db91f206a78af570197f157f4c7372db3ef13470cdfbcdebf576b1#1 \
--tx-out $(cat extended-payment.addr)+100000000000 \
--tx-out $(cat payment.addr)+889999640090 \
--invalid-hereafter 10022040 \
--fee 183849 \
--metadata-json-file metadata.json \
--metadata-json-file metadata2.json \
--metadata-cbor-file metadata3.cbor \
--metadata-cbor-file metadata4.cbor \
--out-file tx002.raw



cardano-cli transaction sign \
--tx-body-file tx002.raw \
--signing-key-file ../keys/payment.skey \
--testnet-magic 3 \
--out-file tx002.signed


cardano-cli transaction submit \
--tx-file tx002.signed \
--testnet-magic 3



cardano-cli query utxo --address "$(cat payment.addr)" --testnet-magic  3 --allegra-era
